Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libmpv2, libgtk-4-1, libadwaita-1-0
Maintainer: Dania Costa <tu@email.com>
Description: Aurora Video Wallpaper
 Animated video wallpaper manager for Linux / GNOME.
 Supports multi-monitor, hardware decoding, and auto-pause.
